[SN]TITLE[SN]
Michael O'Neill: Northern Ireland manager's tips for young players and coaches

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Northern Ireland manager Michael O'Neill believes attitude and application are the most important characteristics in young footballers.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is not supported on this device
Speaking to BBC Get Inspired before Northern Ireland's Euro 2016 campaign, O'Neill also gave his top tips for young coaches.
Northern Ireland face Poland at 17:00 BST on Sunday, 12 June and you can watch it live on BBC TV and listen on BBC Radio 5 live.
